profile:
At Renewable Surfaces, we resurface countertops, bathroom and vanity countertops, garage floors, table tops, desktops, bartops and restaurant tables to look like granite, marble or other natural stone surfaces.
 
Renewable Surfaces give countertops a custom look without the custom price.  We can apply our product directly over Formica, Tile, or most any other type of existing countertop or concrete garage floor.

Renewable Surfaces works with Homeowner Renovations, Commercial Landlords, Property Owners and Restaurants.

Renewable Surfaces offers services in Innisfil, Simcoe County,Muskoka, Barrie, Orillia, and more!
